            . I live in the prosecutrix's house; I had been out for about five minutes - I met the prisoner just by the door, with the soap in his apron; I said, "What have you got?" he said Nothing - I said, "I must look;" he then dropped the soap from his apron - I have inquired and find his family are respectable.</p>
